This was a huge hit with my family and friends! I made it for a small get-together with some friends and family and my mom loved it so much, she requests that I make it every time we have a family picnic. I have made it with pre-cooked chicken pieces from Trader Joe's and by boiling the chicken myself with Tarragon in the water and we like it much better when we cook the chicken ourselves. Also, I found that shredding the chicken by hand instead of cubing it, even though it took longer, allowed the chicken to be more evenly distributed.

